Text: Re Trent Mesa GenTemp data Cc LNotesnsf Mark good set of data please proceed I shall work with this set of data for now and see later if we need to get anything else thanks nagwa Mark Fisher AM To Nagwa nron cc Hollis NRON Subject Trent Mesa GenTemp data Nagwa Im attaching a sample of the output of your request one turbine Please make sure all the fields you need are here The logic I used is as follows Find the moving average of Power KW using a minute record interval For all minute records where the moving average is find the maximum amb temp Find a record where both conditions are true high temphigh power I added a marker for the selected record Make table hours from the marked record should have close to records If either the logic or the fields selected need adjustment let me know Mark Fisher
